                    li Pure Earth. (2019). Fact Sheet: The Toxic Toll of Mercury – Facts, Figures and the Future of “Dancing Cat Fever” Disease
                        a(href= "https://www.pureearth.org/blog/the-toxic-toll-of-mercury-facts-figures-and-the-future-of-dancing-cat-fever-disease/", target="_blank") https://www.pureearth.org/blog/the-toxic-toll-of-mercury-facts-figures-and-the-future-of-dancing-cat-fever-disease/



